BELIEF MOMENTUM AND TRACKING
============================================================
Beliefs can exhibit 'momentum' - tendency to continue in
the same direction. This depends on observation strength.

Tracking belief momentum:
Step  Obs  Belief                    Change     Momentum
 1    0   [0.6  0.25 0.15]  +0.267      -
